---
import Container from "../components/atoms/Container.astro";
import Legals from "../components/sections/Legals.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/index.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section>
    <Container class="pt-28">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-6xl dark:text-light-300 text-primary-900 mb-12 font-bold font-gotham">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <h4 class="sm:text-3xl dark:text-light-200 text-dark-500 mb-4 font-medium font-gotham">Nigeria</h4>

      <div class="w-full border-t pt-6 border-light-500/20 dark:border-dark-300/20">
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-xl text-dark-100">Last updated: 14 April 2024</p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
  <Legals class="mt-8">
    <p>
      At CR3ST Digital Agency Ltd, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your
      personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you interact
      with our website and services.
    </p>
  </Legals>

  <Legals class="mt-8" heading="Information We Collect">
    <p>We may collect personal information, including but not limited to:</p>
    <ul class="mt-2">
      <li>Contact Information: Name, email address, phone number, and other contact details.</li>
      <li>Demographic Information: Location, age, gender, and other demographic data.</li>
      <li>
        Usage Data: Information about how you interact with our website and services, including browsing activity, pages
        visited, and links clicked.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </Legals>

  <Legals class="mt-8" heading="How We Use Your Information">
    <p>We use the information we collect for various purposes, including to:</p>
    <ul class="mt-2">
      <li>Provide and maintain our services.</li>
      <li>Communicate with you about our products, services, and promotions.</li>
      <li>Improve our website and services based on your feedback and usage patterns.</li>
      <li>Prevent fraud and enhance the security of our website and services.</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms of service.</li>
    </ul>
  </Legals>
  <Legals class="mt-8" heading="Information Sharing and Disclosure">
    <p>
      We may share your personal information with third-party service providers, business partners, or affiliates who
      assist us in operating our website and providing our services. We may also disclose your information in response
      to legal requests or to protect our rights, property, or safety.
    </p>
  </Legals>
  <Legals class="mt-8" heading="Data Security">
    <p>
      We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
      However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee
      the absolute security of your data.
    </p>
  </Legals>
  <Legals class="mt-8" heading="Changes to This Policy">
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or to comply with legal
      requirements. We encourage you to review this page periodically for the latest information on our privacy
      practices.
    </p>
  </Legals>
  <Legals class="mt-10">
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns about our  Privacy Policy or our handling of your personal information, please contact us at <a
        href="mailto:info@cr3st.com"
        class="text-secondary">info@cr3st.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </Legals>
  <div class="mb-64"></div>
</Layout>
<style>
  li {
    list-style-type: disc;
    list-style-position: inside;
  }
  a {
    display: inline;
  }
</style>
